OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FBetween 1961 and 1987 over 24,000
OL,7,Fyoung offenders were held at Medomsley
OL,8,FDetention Centre.
OL,10,FMore than 1,800 of those have since
OL,11,Freported that they were either
OL,12,Fphysically or sexually abused while
OL,13,Fbeing detained at the facility near
OL,14,FConsett, County Durham.
OL,16,FEight former members of staff have
OL,17,Fbeen jailed for their role in the
OL,18,Fabuse after two investigations by
OL,19,FDurham Constabulary - Operation Halter
OL,20,Fand Operation Seabrook.
