OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FA fresh investigation by the Prisons
OL,7,Fand Probation Ombudsman (PPO),
OL,8,FOperation Deerness, is now
OL,9,Finvestigating what the authorities
OL,10,Fknew about the abuse that took place
OL,11,Fand whether there were opportunities
OL,12,Fto stop it.
OL,14,FHere, ITV Tyne Tees looks back at the
OL,15,Fhistory of the centre and the abuse
OL,16,Fscandal that later emerged.
