OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FThe facility closed in 1988.
OL,8,FOperation Halter - First police
OL,9,Finvestigation
OL,11,FDurham Constabulary first investigated
OL,12,Fallegations of sexual abuse against
OL,13,Finmates at the centre during the early
OL,14,F2000s.
OL,16,FOperation Halter resulted in former
OL,17,FMedomsley Detention Centre cook
OL,18,FNeville Husband being convicted of
OL,19,Fsexually abusing five teenagers in
OL,20,FFebruary 2003 before admitting four
OL,21,Ffurther attacks in 2005.
