OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FOfficer Leslie Johnson was also jailed
OL,7,Ffor sexual abuse in 2005.
OL,9,FOperation Seabrook - Investigations
OL,10,Freopen
OL,12,FIn August 2013, 25 years after
OL,13,FMedomsley Detention Centre closed, a
OL,14,Fvictim came forward to report being
OL,15,Fabused at the facility.
OL,17,FIn response, Durham Constabulary
OL,18,Flaunched Operation Seabrook, reopening
OL,19,Finvestigations into allegations at the
OL,20,Fcentre. It became one of the country's
OL,21,Fbiggest abuse investigations.
