OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FAccording to the force's website,
OL,7,F1,848 men have come forward to report
OL,8,Fallegations of abuse while at the
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FThis included allegations of serious
OL,12,Fphysical abuse which resulted in
OL,13,Finmates suffering broken bones, sexual
OL,14,Fassaults and psychological abuse.
OL,16,FSeabrook detectives identified 32
OL,17,Fsuspects who were still alive and six
OL,18,Fhave since been convicted in court.
