OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FIn 2019, five former prison officers
OL,7,Fwere jailed for more than 18 years in
OL,8,Ftotal for abusing former inmates at
OL,9,Fthe centre following three separate
OL,10,Fcrown court trials. They were
OL,11,FChristopher Onslow, John McGee, Alan
OL,12,FBramley, Kevin Blakeley and Brian
OL,13,FJohnson Greenwell.
OL,15,FIn 2023, Alexander Flavell was found
OL,16,Fguilty of indecent assault of a young
OL,17,Finmate and misconduct in a public
OL,18,Foffice, bringing the operation to an
OL,19,Fend.
OL,21,FWhat is happening now?
