OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday 28 February, the PPO
OL,7,Fannounced they had begun their own
OL,8,Finvestigation, Operation Deerness,
OL,9,Fwhich will look to uncover how much
OL,10,Fthe authorities knew about what was
OL,11,Fgoing on at Medomsley Detention Centre
OL,12,Fat the time.
OL,14,FThe investigation has been
OL,15,Fcommissioned by the Justice Secretary
OL,16,Fbut it will work independently of the
OL,17,Fgovernment, police and the prison
OL,18,Fservice.
