OL,3,CWhat happened at Medomsley Detention
OL,4,CCentre?
OL,6,FLead investigating officer Richard
OL,7,FTucker made a direct appeal for anyone
OL,8,Fwith information to speak out about
OL,9,Fwhat they witnessed or knew at the
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FThe PPO will produce a report of their
OL,13,Ffindings that they hope will provide
OL,14,Fanswers to those who suffered abuse
OL,15,Fand prevent anything like it from
OL,16,Fhappening again.
